name: DW Fake Breasts
description:
This is a LoRA that gives girls big fake breasts as shown in the pictures.

This LoRA was trained on Deliberate and works well with the realism checkpoints that I've tried it with such as MajicMix and Deliberate of course. It also works quite well with the 2.5D models like revAnimated and AbyssOrangeMix. There are sample images using each of these models.

The model doesn't have any specific trigger words but a prompt like "big breasts" along with changing the strength of the LoRA can be used to achieve the desired result. For my desires I went with a strength of 0.75: <lora:HunbrstsV3:0.75>. The name of the LoRA file is confusing, sorry.

To produce some of the images I've made, I used the help of hires fix with the 4x-Ultrasharp upscaler and AfterDetailer which I used caphalorthrow's BimbostyeFiveU to get the bimbo lips.
